text: Pithecopus oreades is a frog that lives in Brazil. It lives high in the hills. Scientists have seen it more than 900 meters above sea level. Scientists have seen it up in the mountains, between 280 and 1000 meters above sea level. This frog lays eggs in streams, where the tadpoles swim in pools. ==References== Category:Frogs of South America
title: Pithecopus oreades
